

This extension shows ZCASH value priced in Bitcoin and American Dollars(BTC, USD).
ZCASH (https://z.cash/) is a cryptocurrency that offers total payment confidentiality, while still maintaining a decentralized network using a public blockchain.
Values are refreshed every 4 minutes.
Values are based on data provided by 'www.coinmarketcap.com' API and are most likely appropriate, but don't have to be.
No special permissions are needed to install this extension.
Tips appreciated:
